Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.44,0:22:11.56,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虚実は花と咲き乱れ実る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.99,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}夢の瑕疵の　唾棄すべき腑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:26.15,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}手をかけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.45,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}命を以て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:38.12,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}蒼白に開く指　まみえる前に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:44.08,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もしもおもえが　暗殺者ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:50.49,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}迷い　嫉み　打ち砕くことができようか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.78,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悶絶せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:23:00.24,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}堕落するときは　いっそ見事に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:03.70,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}血を吐き　毒に塗れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:06.84,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}奈落へと向かわん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:11.89,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}其処でしか見えない天を仰ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.51,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}灼け爛れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:17.69,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明日を嗤えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:59.94,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一旦被蛇所魅惑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:03.36,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}便會直直墜入蛇道深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:06.44,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}憎惡纍纍不堪重負
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.44,0:22:11.56,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虛實如鮮花遍地綻放結實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.99,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}卻是夢的瑕疵 遭人唾棄的臟腑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:26.15,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}搭上這雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.45,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}賭上這條命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:38.12,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即將面對時 蒼白地打開手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:44.08,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如果你是暗殺者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:50.49,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否就能粉碎迷惑心 嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.78,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}痛苦昏厥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:23:00.24,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}當墮落之時 不如徹底點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:03.70,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}口吐鮮血 身塗劇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:06.84,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}向著地獄直奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:11.89,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望在地獄才能一見的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.51,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}身形漸漸灼燒潰爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:17.69,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}對未來嗤笑不已
